  "prompt": "Are Quora blog posts ever published on media sites, or just Quora answers?",
  "response": "Quora content, including answers, is sometimes republished on media sites, but this typically involves Quora answers rather than blog posts. Quora blogs, a feature that allowed users to write longer, article-style content, were discontinued in 2021, so any references to Quora blog posts being published elsewhere would be outdated. Instead, it's common for media sites to collaborate with Quora to syndicate popular or insightful answers, often through partnerships or content-sharing agreements.",
